OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy in
OL,6,Fthe northwest with outbreaks of light
OL,7,Frain and drizzle possible. The
OL,8,Fsoutheast will stay dry with late
OL,9,Fevening sunny spells then clear spells
OL,10,Fovernight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FAnother cloudy day in the
OL,13,Fnorthwest with light rain and drizzle
OL,14,Fpossible. Drier and mostly cloudy in
OL,15,Fthe southeast with some sunny spells
OL,16,Fbreaking through.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
