OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FA
OL,6,Fmostly cloudy few days with outbreaks
OL,7,Fof rain and drizzle, perhaps heavier
OL,8,Fon Friday and Saturday. Drier with
OL,9,Fbright intervals in the southeast.
OL,10,FFresher winds Thursday and Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
